*Uzima* se u obzir njegov stav (His opinion is taken into consideration).
*Uzima*o je knjigu i otišao (He took the book and left).
*Uzimam* svoje stvari i idem (I am taking my things and leaving).
*Uzela* je novčanik iz džepa (She took the wallet from the pocket).
*Uzim*o samo ono što mu je potrebno (He was taking only what he needed).